{
  "id": "adv_card_rei_12_01",
  "title": "一ノ瀬怜 1話 不思議な力で行きたい場所へ",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_office-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "env_adv_3d_office-01-000-noon",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "sfx",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_book-01.m4a",
      "startTime": 0.4666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_12_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_12_01-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "おや？　あれは……怜？　さっきから熱心に\n雑誌を読んでいるが、何を読んでるんだ？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "おや？　あれは……怜？　さっきから熱心に\n雑誌を読んでいるが、何を読んでるんだ？",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 6.4333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_12_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_12_01-rei001.m4a",
      "text": "これは世界中の不思議と謎を紹介する情報誌です\n今月号は宇宙人特集なんですよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "これは世界中の不思議と謎を紹介する情報誌です\n今月号は宇宙人特集なんですよ",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 14.3666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_12_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_12_01-rei002.m4a",
      "text": "知ってますか？　約45万年前、古代シュメール文明に\n太陽系第12惑星ニビルから宇宙人が飛来したんです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "知ってますか？　約45万年前、古代シュメール文明に\n太陽系第12惑星ニビルから宇宙人が飛来したんです",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 23.3,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_12_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_12_01-rei003.m4a",
      "text": "アヌンナキと呼ばれたその宇宙人の遺伝子操作によって\n人類が作られたという説があって……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "アヌンナキと呼ばれたその宇宙人の遺伝子操作によって\n人類が作られたという説があって……",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 32.3666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_12_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_12_01-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "ちょ、ちょっと待ってくれ、一体どうしたんだ？\n怜はオカルトに興味があったのか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "ちょ、ちょっと待ってくれ、一体どうしたんだ？\n怜はオカルトに興味があったのか？",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 38.8333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_12_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_12_01-rei004.m4a",
      "text": "いえ……最近、宇宙人、未来人、超能力者と\n関わることがあってそれでいろいろ調べていたんです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "いえ……最近、宇宙人、未来人、超能力者と\n関わることがあってそれでいろいろ調べていたんです",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 47.2,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_12_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_12_01-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "……何と関わったって？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "……何と関わったって？",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 52.2666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_12_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_12_01-rei005.m4a",
      "text": "宇宙人、未来人、超能力者です\nこの間話した『涼宮ハルヒ』がいる高校での話です",
      "translations": {
        "en": "宇宙人、未来人、超能力者です\nこの間話した『涼宮ハルヒ』がいる高校での話です",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 59.5666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_12_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_12_01-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "そういえば怜が今着ている衣装、千紗が作ったんだよな\n確か、千紗が夢の中で着ていた制服を再現したとか……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "そういえば怜が今着ている衣装、千紗が作ったんだよな\n確か、千紗が夢の中で着ていた制服を再現したとか……",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 68.9666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_12_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_12_01-rei006.m4a",
      "text": "だから、夢じゃありません\nこれはハルヒがいた北高の制服です",
      "translations": {
        "en": "だから、夢じゃありません\nこれはハルヒがいた北高の制服です",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 77.6,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_12_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_12_01-rei007.m4a",
      "text": "私は、千紗、芽衣、沙季と一緒に\nこの制服を着て同じ高校に通っていたんです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "私は、千紗、芽衣、沙季と一緒に\nこの制服を着て同じ高校に通っていたんです",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 84.3666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_12_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_12_01-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "他の三人も同じことを言っていたな……みんなで\n同じ夢を見るなんて不思議なこともあるんだな",
      "translations": {
        "en": "他の三人も同じことを言っていたな……みんなで\n同じ夢を見るなんて不思議なこともあるんだな",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 93.0333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_12_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_12_01-rei008.m4a",
      "text": "だから、夢じゃないって言ってるじゃないですか\nパラレルワールドって知ってますか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "だから、夢じゃないって言ってるじゃないですか\nパラレルワールドって知ってますか？",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 101.2666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_12_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_12_01-rei009.m4a",
      "text": "過去のある時点から分岐した\n平行して存在する世界があるという考え方です",
      "translations": {
        "en": "過去のある時点から分岐した\n平行して存在する世界があるという考え方です",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 106.6874612575,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_12_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_12_01-rei010.m4a",
      "text": "私とみんなが夢だと思っていたのは、こことは違う世界\n……パラレルワールドだったのかもしれません",
      "translations": {
        "en": "私とみんなが夢だと思っていたのは、こことは違う世界\n……パラレルワールドだったのかもしれません",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 117.7666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_12_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_12_01-koh006.m4a",
      "text": "なるほど、つまりこういうことだな\n仕事が忙し過ぎて疲れている怜達は集団幻覚を……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "なるほど、つまりこういうことだな\n仕事が忙し過ぎて疲れている怜達は集団幻覚を……",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 124.5333348592,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_12_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_12_01-rei011.m4a",
      "text": "違います！\nちゃんと話を聞いていましたか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "違います！\nちゃんと話を聞いていましたか？",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 130.5666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_12_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_12_01-koh007.m4a",
      "text": "す、すまない……だが、たまたま似た夢を見て\n同じだと思い込んでいるだけじゃないのか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "す、すまない……だが、たまたま似た夢を見て\n同じだと思い込んでいるだけじゃないのか？",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 138.1666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_12_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_12_01-rei012.m4a",
      "text": "それは、そうかもしれませんが……\nいえ……普通はそう考えるのが自然ですよね……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "それは、そうかもしれませんが……\nいえ……普通はそう考えるのが自然ですよね……",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 145.6000030518,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_12_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_12_01-rei013.m4a",
      "text": "でも、仮に夢だったとしても\n全員で同じ夢を見るなんて偶然とは思えません",
      "translations": {
        "en": "でも、仮に夢だったとしても\n全員で同じ夢を見るなんて偶然とは思えません",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 153.3333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_12_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_12_01-rei014.m4a",
      "text": "だから世界中の不思議な出来事を調べて\nパラレルワールドを証明しようと思ったんですが……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "だから世界中の不思議な出来事を調べて\nパラレルワールドを証明しようと思ったんですが……",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 161.3,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_12_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_12_01-rei015.m4a",
      "text": "でも、やっぱり難しいですね。いくら調べても\nパラレルワールドの存在は証明出来なくて……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "でも、やっぱり難しいですね。いくら調べても\nパラレルワールドの存在は証明出来なくて……",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 170.6,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_12_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_12_01-rei016.m4a",
      "text": "時間が経つにつれて、記憶も曖昧になってきて……\n本当にあったことなのか自信がなくなってきました",
      "translations": {
        "en": "時間が経つにつれて、記憶も曖昧になってきて……\n本当にあったことなのか自信がなくなってきました",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 179.0000071208,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_12_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_12_01-rei017.m4a",
      "text": "やっぱりあれは、ただの夢だったのかしら……\nあの学校も、涼宮ハルヒも、全部夢なのかしら……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "やっぱりあれは、ただの夢だったのかしら……\nあの学校も、涼宮ハルヒも、全部夢なのかしら……",
        "id": ""
      },
